snippet.title: Best VGM 2273 - Castlevania III - Aquarius
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 696 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VpyUtWCMrb4
Best VGM 1420 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s4pG2_UOel4

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
Castlevania III : Dracula's Curse (1990)
Aquarius
Hidenori Maezawa, Jun Funahashi & Yukie Morimoto
